## Success Criteria

Phase 4 succeeds when:
- [ ] All tests pass (100% pass rate)
- [ ] Coverage meets thresholds:
  - Business logic: ≥95%
  - Application layer: ≥85%
  - Infrastructure: ≥80%
- [ ] Build succeeds
- [ ] No integration issues detected
